<plot>This was a controversial documentary about the life and death of an IRA woman, Mairead Farrell, by the British SAS in Gibraltar. The centre-piece of the documentary is about Farrell's life and how circumstances drove her to embrace Irish Republican violence that inevitably was to lead to her death and, in some quarters, martyrdom.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?134153</url></doc>
